;}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1683:\"<p><strong>Product</strong>:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wordpress-conditional-display-for-mobile/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress Mobile Detect</a></p>\n<p><strong>Question</strong>:</p>\n<p>I am looking for a solution to be able to serve different content to mobile and tablet - desktop. Your plugin seems to be one of the few around, but I build my sites with Siteorigin Page Builder, so I guess the shortcode wrapping will not work.</p>\n<p>Is there any other way of getting this functionality that you can recommend, as far as integrating with a page builder?</p>\n<p><span id=\"more-5718\"></span></p>\n<p><strong>Answer</strong>:</p>\n<p>Siteorigin Page Builder supports shortcode.</p>\n<p>In Siteorigin page editor, click the button \"Add Widget\", find the widget \"Text\", then you can edit the Text widget content and enter the shortcode.</p>\n<p><a class=\"wplightbox\" href=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/siteorigin-shortcode.png\"><img src=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/siteorigin-shortcode-600x296.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"296\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5719\" srcset=\"https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/siteorigin-shortcode-600x296.png 600w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/siteorigin-shortcode-240x118.png 240w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/siteorigin-shortcode-75x37.png 75w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/siteorigin-shortcode-500x247.png 500w, https://www.wonderplugin.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/siteorigin-shortcode.png 693w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a> </p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n